{"tid":2477215,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"是咁的，整左個小說平台","createTime":"2021-04-06T06:23:39.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-14T13:35:03.000Z","uid":69481,"like":21,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"9fac2f5c4ee268f1bb691573f55e6279c7340df0","tid":2477215,"uid":69481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T06:23:39.000Z","msg":"是咁的，整左個小說平台，學嘢為主，多人用最好，拎黎見工都好啲。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmfAxmLx15HV65FwcbTBmycUvQ5oydZBqJxuhasKe7ZpkH?filename=Y28x73t.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY28x73t.png&h=2516d90f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n因為唔識Design，Layout 直接抄<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，啲色都比較單調。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>- Security</strong><br />\n基本嘅Security 應該都做左，但唔知有冇咩做得唔好，Password 建議用Browser suggest，唔驚唔記得password的話，Email 可以亂打 ( 可以改 )，只要format 啱就得，唔需要認證。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>- 成為作者</strong><br />\n註冊後點擊左上粒制打開Menu，然後點擊「成為作者」，成功後再點擊「寫文」，就可以進入管理頁面。<br />\n如果想大量上傳現有作品，又有統一格式 ( e.g 檔案名係章節名，檔案內容係章節內容 ) 可以tg 我幫手上傳<br />\n<br />\n<strong>- 有冇App？</strong><br />\n暫時冇，可以用住手機Browser 「加至主畫面」功能，iOS 得Safari 有，Android Chrome 一定有，其他Browser唔肯定。<br />\n有試緊整App，但唔捨得比錢，可能最後都係放個APK 出黎就算。<br />\n<br />\nLink:&nbsp;<a href=\"http://taisiusyut.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftaisiusyut.com&d=PGvktPFvO8uhCwWWOTiXte4Wvb5rKEvwepesSl%2FR16E%3D&h=9cc09573\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://taisiusyut.com</a><br />\nSource Code:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/taisiusyut/taisiusyut\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Ftaisiusyut%2Ftaisiusyut&d=PGvktPFvO8uhCwWWOTiXte4Wvb5rKEvwepesSl%2FR16E%3D&h=58eb2c8b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/taisiusyut/taisiusyut</a><br />\nTelegram群組: <a href=\"https://t.me/taisiusyut\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftaisiusyut&d=PGvktPFvO8uhCwWWOTiXte4Wvb5rKEvwepesSl%2FR16E%3D&h=a1b63edd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/taisiusyut</a><br />\n私人Telegram: <a href=\"https://t.me/Pong420\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FPong420&d=PGvktPFvO8uhCwWWOTiXte4Wvb5rKEvwepesSl%2FR16E%3D&h=5d9a331f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/Pong420</a><br />\n<br />\n冇人用都好，應該都會launch 一年左右，摺左的話作品都會保留一段時間，作者可以搵我拎返，當然最好自己backup啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbca68bfabb629b2dbc124e751173cc074e17f83","tid":2477215,"uid":39630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T06:25:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/miracle.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/miracle.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/miracle.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a39ba7c2708e89bb91628a8cb5f27ca2d5b5cdb","tid":2477215,"uid":376497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T07:09:25.000Z","msg":"有無插圖功能?我本身會自畫封面/場境之類。"},{"pid":"cfe464dcc154b6b773e98a9965319b36765e4667","tid":2477215,"uid":69481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a39ba7c2708e89bb91628a8cb5f27ca2d5b5cdb","tid":2477215,"uid":376497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T07:09:25.000Z","msg":"有無插圖功能?我本身會自畫封面/場境之類。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T07:21:58.000Z","msg":"冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果冇其他feedback 會試下加"},{"pid":"39db1df6627fb1471227dc18c6e6c49c308b9adb","tid":2477215,"uid":56984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T07:25:30.000Z","msg":"pushhhhh"},{"pid":"172655504eed3aaf9f64dc8955a9f9b1a4fc98f5","tid":2477215,"uid":174504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T07:26:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推"},{"pid":"a790ff322dfcd834ddec5bb982c54dad73a26604","tid":2477215,"uid":133865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T08:21:34.000Z","msg":"<img src